## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible strategies for enhancing creativity. Additionally, the effectiveness of these strategies can vary among individuals due to personal preferences and learning styles. Further research, including empirical studies, could provide more comprehensive insights into creativity enhancement for college students.

